Ugandan Leader Yoweri Museveni Appoints New Vice President, Prime Minister

-- B y   F r e d   O j a m b o
-- 
2011-05-24T10:26:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/ugandan-leader-yoweri-museveni-appoints-new-vice-president-prime-minister.html
Ugandan President Yoweri Museveni
named former Speaker of Parliament Edward Kiwanuka Ssekandi as
vice president and former Security Minister Amama Mbabazi as
prime minister, Ofwono Opondo, the deputy spokesman of the
ruling National Resistance Movement, said by phone today from
the capital, Kampala.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Ojambo in Kampala at 
 fojambo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  